<p class="text-xs text-slate-500 px-6 py-4 border-t border-slate-100">Indicative costs for Mumbai (BKC, Lower Parel, Goregaon, Andheri). Managed office costs include rent, furniture, internet, housekeeping, and maintenance. Coworking costs may exclude meeting rooms, printing, and after-hours access.</p>
